      "id": "PopularPost317774",
      "post_content": "I actually like this one over [Sword of Fire and Ice](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sword of Fire and Ice). It's not a matter of power (no matter how much I worry that people might be over-valorizing card draw; it's just a catalyst, not a weapon in and of itself!), just that the creature recovery is the sort of thing that REALLY draws my interest.  \n  \nOn another note, it's confirmed for Modern Masters along with the UR sword. With the same sort of art as the Scars of Mirrodin block swords, to boot. (The bad news? They got \"promoted\" to mythic.)  ",
      "posted_by": "SkyknightXi",
